The paper proposes a framework for data representation using semi-supervised learning and factorization techniques. The paper focuses on enhancing the discrimination of the representation by incorporating label information and preserving manifold structures. This makes it likely to belong to categories such as cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
